BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:Category: Yoga\nInstructor: Lex B.\nA strong vinyasa class focused on strength\, endurance\, and stability. Arm balances\, inversions\, and innovative transitions make these classes both fun and challenging!We look to provide all of our students with a quality experience. To help us meet that goal and secure your spot\, you are strongly encouraged to register before the start of class.\nhttps://portal.movementgyms.com/portland/programs/power-vinyasa?course=U2Vzc2lvbjoxNDUyOTcyOTA=&date=2026-07-02
DTEND:20260703T020000Z
LOCATION:Movement Portland
