BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:Category: Yoga\nInstructor: Shannon L.\nSlow your nervous system down. Props\, rather than your muscles\, are used to support your body in only five or six poses\, allowing you to relax and rest completely. May incorporate meditation and breathing exercises. Perfect when you're feeling drained or stressed.\nhttps://portal.movementgyms.com/portland/programs/restorative-yoga?course=U2Vzc2lvbjoxMTUzNTI3MDM=&date=2026-06-09
DTEND:20260610T033000Z
LOCATION:Movement Portland
